title: Новости сегодня Узбекистан нашёл крупное месторождение газа — заявление президента взорвало сети!
description:
Срочные новости В Узбекистане найдено новое крупное месторождение природного газа на плато Устюрт, в Каракалпакстане. Скважина пробурена на рекордную глубину более 6 500 метров, и эксперты уже называют это открытие одним из самых значимых событий для энергетического рынка региона.

Это открытие может изменить энергетическую карту Центральной Азии и повлиять на мировые цены на газ. В условиях глобального дефицита энергоресурсов и геополитической напряжённости, такие находки играют стратегическую роль.

Президент Шавкат Мирзиёев отметил, что это важный шаг к энергетической независимости страны. Возможно, в ближайшем будущем Узбекистан станет одним из ключевых игроков на газовом рынке.

Следите за новостями, чтобы не пропустить, как это открытие повлияет на мировую экономику, политику и международные отношения.

description:
बिहार चुनाव को लेकर बड़ी खबर आ रही है। भोजपुरी एक्टर और बीजेपी नेता पवन सिंह ने चुनाव लड़ने से इनकार कर दिया है। उन्होंने खुद को पार्टी का सच्चा सिपाही बताया और कहा कि उन्होंने चुनाव लड़ने के लिए पार्टी ज्वाइन नहीं की थी। कुछ दिनों पहले ही पवन सिंह दोबारा बीजेपी के साथ शामिल हुए हैं। उनके चुनाव लड़ने की चर्चाएं जोरों पर थी। उन्हें आरा विधानसभा सीट से मैदान में उतारने की अटकलें लगाई जा रही थी। हालांकि इस बीच उनका और उनकी पत्नी ज्योति सिंह का विवाद गहराा गया। पवन सिंह ने X पर एक पोस्ट के जरिए चुनाव नहीं लड़ने के अपने फैसले की जानकारी दी है। उन्होंने केंद्रीय गृह मंत्री अमित शाह संग तस्वीर साझा की और लिखा, “मैं पवन सिंह अपने भोजपुरीया समाज से बताना चाहता हूं कि मैं बिहार विधानसभा चुनाव लड़ने के लिए पार्टी ज्वाइन नहीं किया था और ना ही मुझे विधानसभा चुनाव लड़ना है। मैं पार्टी का सच्चा सिपाही हूं और रहूंगा।”

title: Bihar Election Survey | क्या है बिहार का ताजा सर्वे, जानिए | Bihar Politics| NDA | AajTak LIVE
description:
आज तक के खास कार्यक्रम 'बिहार का मिज़ाज' में बिहार विधानसभा चुनाव से पहले हुए सर्वे के नतीजों पर गहन चर्चा हुई. इस दौरान एनडीए और महागठबंधन के बीच कड़े चुनावी मुकाबले का विश्लेषण किया गया. सर्वे में मुख्यमंत्री पद के लिए तेजस्वी यादव 36.2% लोकप्रियता के साथ सबसे आगे रहे, जबकि प्रशांत किशोर की लोकप्रियता में 23.2% की वृद्धि दर्ज की गई. नीतीश कुमार की लोकप्रियता 15.9% पर आ गई. एनडीए गठबंधन के भीतर सीट बंटवारे को लेकर जारी घमासान पर भी विशेष ध्यान दिया गया, जहाँ 48.6% लोगों ने इसे सबसे मुश्किल बताया और 35.1% का मानना था कि चिराग पासवान पाला बदल सकते हैं. कार्यक्रम में तेजस्वी यादव के 30 लाख नौकरियों के वादे और एनडीए की महिलाओं को 10,000 रुपये देने की योजना पर तीखी बहस हुई. बेरोजगारी और पलायन जैसे मुद्दों पर जनता का भरोसा महागठबंधन (36.5%) पर एनडीए (34.3%) से अधिक दिखा. कांग्रेस प्रवक्ता अभय दुबे ने एनडीए के अंतर्विरोधों पर तंज कसा और सर्वे की विश्वसनीयता पर भी सवाल उठाए. भ्रष्टाचार, महिला सुरक्षा, और नीतीश कुमार के बार-बार पाला बदलने जैसे मुद्दे भी चर्चा का केंद्र रहे. सर्वे के अनुसार, एनडीए को 40.2% और महागठबंधन को 38.3% वोट मिलने का अनुमान है, जबकि जन सुराज 13.3% वोट के साथ एक महत्वपूर्ण कारक बन रही है. लगभग 40% लोगों को संदेह है कि एनडीए जीतने के बाद नीतीश कुमार को मुख्यमंत्री नहीं बनाएगी.

title: Chaos in France as Macron reappoint Lecornu days after he quit | DW News
description:
French President Emmanuel Macron has reappointed Sebastien Lecornu as prime minister - just days after he quit over political infighting. Lecornu must form a government and present a new budget to a hung parliament by Monday. Opposition lawmakers have criticized his reappointment, with parties calling for snap elections and Macron's resignation. Divisions over reducing France's soaring debt have toppled Lecornu's two predecessors.

title: Ultimatum Menteri Israel, Ancam Gulingkan Pemerintahan Netanyahu jika Hamas Tak Dihancurkan
description:
Download aplikasi berita TribunX di Play Store atau App Store untuk dapatkan pengalaman baru

SURYA.CO.ID - Menteri Keamanan Nasional Israel, Itamar Ben-Gvir, memperingatkan bahwa partainya akan menggulingkan pemerintahan Perdana Menteri Benjamin Netanyahu.

Jika Hamas tidak benar-benar dibubarkan seusai perjanjian gencatan senjata Gaza.

Peringatan itu disampaikan Ben-Gvir pada Kamis (9/10), hanya beberapa jam sebelum kabinet Netanyahu menggelar sidang.

Untuk memutuskan rencana gencatan senjata dan pembebasan tawanan dalam fase pertama kesepakatan tersebut.

Ia menegaskan bahwa tidak akan mentolerir jika Hamas masih eksis dengan nama atau bentuk lain.

title: Marathi News : Ajit Pawar आणि BJP यांच्यामध्ये बिनसत चाललय का ?| Maharashtra Politics
description:
#vishaychbhari  #marathinews #ajitpawar #devendrafadanvis 

Marathi News | Maharashtra Politics | Ajit Pawar | Devendra Fadnavis

The elections to local bodies, known as mini-assembly in political circles, are now just around the corner. Perhaps after Diwali, the trumpet of elections to municipalities, nagar panchayats, zilla parishads, panchayat samiti and metropolitan municipalities in the state is likely to sound. Since it has been about three to five years since the term of many local bodies expired, local-level leaders and leadership groups are ready for these elections. At the state level, the ruling grand alliance and the opposition party Mahavikas Aghadi have also started preparations for these elections. At present, the preparations of the ruling grand alliance seem to be more vigorous than those of the opposition party Mahavikas Aghadi. There are differences on many issues such as whether to fight together in the Mahavikas Aghadi or take decisions at the local level, whether to take Raj Thackeray's MNS along with them. However, there is some clarity in the grand alliance on whether to fight together or separately. However, there are signs of a large-scale infiltration in the local body elections between the BJP, the main constituent party in the grand alliance, and Ajit Pawar's Nationalist Congress. Here's a look at the exact issues on which differences are likely to arise between the BJP and Ajit's Nationalist Party, and how it could affect the grand alliance. Here's a look at where the two parties could contest separately.

राजकीय वर्तुळात मिनी विधानसभा म्हणून ओळखल्या जाणाऱ्या स्थानिक स्वराज्य संस्थांच्या निवडणुका आता अगदी तोंडावर आल्या आहेत. कदाचित दिवाळीनंतर राज्यातील नगर पालिका, नगर पंचायती, जिल्हा परिषदा, पंचायत समित्या आणि महानगरपालिकांच्या निवडणुकांचे बिगुल वाजण्याची शक्यता आहे. अनेक स्थानिक स्वराज्य संस्थांची मुदत संपून सुमारे तीन ते पाच वर्षं झालेली असल्याने स्थानिक पातळीवरचे पुढारी आणि नेतेमंडळी या निवडणुकांसाठी सज्ज झाली आहे. तर राज्य पातळीवर सत्ताधारी महायुती आणि विरोधी पक्ष असलेल्या महाविकास आघाडीतील घटक पक्षांनीही या निवडणुकांसाठी जोरदार तयारी सुरू केली आहे. त्यात सध्यातरी विरोधी पक्षांतील महाविकास आघाडीच्या तुलनेत सत्ताधारी महायुतीची तयारी अधिक जोरदार दिसत आहे. महाविकास आघाडीत एकत्र लढायचं की स्थानिक पातळीवर निर्णय घ्यायचे, राज ठाकरेंच्या मनसेला सोबत घ्यायचं का, अशा अनेक मुद्द्यांवरून मतभेद दिसून येत आहेत. तर महायुतीमध्ये मात्र एकत्र लढणार की स्वतंत्र याबाबत काही प्रमाणात स्पष्टता दिसत आहे. मात्र असं असलं तरी महायुतीमधील प्रमुख घटक पक्ष असलेला भाजपा आणि अजित पवार यांच्या राष्ट्रवादी काँग्रेसमध्ये स्थानिक स्वराज्य संस्थांच्या निवडणुकांवरून मोठ्या प्रमाणात घुसफूस होण्याची चिन्हे दिसत आहेत. भाजपा आणि अजितदादांच्या राष्ट्रवादीमध्ये नेमक्या कोणत्या मुद्द्यावरून मतभेद उफाळण्याची शक्यता आहे, तसेच त्याचा महायुतीवर काय परिणाम होऊ शकतो. हे दोन्ही पक्ष कोणकोणत्या ठिकाणी स्वतंत्रपणे लढू शकतात, याचा घेतलेला हा आढावा.

description:
મીડિયા અહેવાલ મુજબ, બ્રિટિશ સરકારે આ કરારને તેના સંરક્ષણ ક્ષેત્ર અને ભારત સાથે વ્યૂહાત્મક સંબંધોને ગાઢ બનાવવા માટે એક ઐતિહાસિક પગલું ગણાવ્યું છે. આ મિસાઇલોનું ઉત્પાદન ઉત્તરી આયર્લૅન્ડમાં થેલ્સના પ્લાન્ટમાં કરવામાં આવશે. બ્રિટિશ અધિકારીઓએ જણાવ્યું છે કે, આ કરાર યુક્રેનને શસ્ત્રો પૂરા પાડતાં એક જ પ્લાન્ટમાં હાલમાં કાર્યરત લગભગ 700 બ્રિટિશ નોકરીઓનું રક્ષણ કરશે. આ પગલું ભારત-યુકે કોમ્પ્લેક્સ વેપન્સ પાર્ટનરશિપમાં એક મહત્ત્વપૂર્ણ સફળતા દર્શાવે છે, જેની ચર્ચા બંને દેશો લાંબા સમયથી કરી રહ્યા છે.

ભારત-બ્રિટનની ડિફેન્સ ભાગીદારી

મુંબઈ સમિટમાં, બંને નેતાઓએ ભારત-યુકે વેપાર સંબંધોની પણ સમીક્ષા કરી હતી. તાજેતરનો મુક્ત વેપાર કરાર (FTA) હવે સંરક્ષણ અને ટૅક્નોલૉજી સહયોગને નવી ગતિ આપી રહ્યો છે. યુકેએ ભારત સાથે નૌકાદળના જહાજો માટે ઈલેક્ટ્રિક એન્જિન ટૅક્નોલૉજી પર એક નવા કરારની પણ જાહેરાત કરી છે. જેનું પ્રારંભિક મૂલ્ય £250 મિલિયન છે. આ પહેલ બંને દેશો વચ્ચે બહુપક્ષીય ભાગીદારીને વધુ મજબૂત બનાવશે. આ અંગે પીએમ નરેન્દ્ર મોદીએ જણાવ્યું હતું કે આ ફક્ત એક વેપાર કરાર નથી, પરંતુ વિશ્વની બે અગ્રણી અર્થવ્યવસ્થાઓ વચ્ચે વહેંચાયેલ પ્રગતિ, વહેંચાયેલ સમૃદ્ધિ અને વહેંચાયેલ લોકો માટે માર્ગદર્શક બ્લુપ્રિન્ટ છે. બજારની પહોંચની સાથે આ કરાર બંને દેશોમાં નાના અને મધ્યમ ઉદ્યોગો(MSMEs)ને સશક્ત બનાવશે અને લાખો યુવાનો માટે રોજગારીની નવી તકો ખોલશે.

પીએમ મોદીએ આગળ કહ્યું કે, વૈશ્વિક અસ્થિરતાના આ સમયગાળામાં ચાલુ કેલેન્ડર વર્ષ ભારત-યુકે સંબંધો માટે મજબૂત વર્ષ સાબિત થયું છે. આ વર્ષે જુલાઈમાં યુકેની મારી મુલાકાત દરમિયાન અમે ઐતિહાસિક વ્યાપકધોરણે આર્થિક અને વેપાર કરાર (CETA) પર સર્વસંમતિ સાધી હતી. હું આ ઐતિહાસિક સિદ્ધિ માટે મારા મિત્ર વડાપ્રધાન સ્ટાર્મરના સમર્પણ અને યોગદાનની ખૂબ પ્રશંસા કરું છું.

बिहार महागठबंधन में सीटों का बंटवारा लगभग तय हो गया है। माले को 19, भाकपा को 8 और माकपा को 4 सीटें मिल सकती हैं। हालांकि माले पर 4 सीटें छोड़ने का दबाव है, जिन पर राजद और कांग्रेस चुनाव लड़ना चाहती हैं। भाकपा और माकपा भी कुछ अतिरिक्त सीटों की मांग कर रहे हैं। कांग्रेस और वीआईपी की सीटों को लेकर बातचीत जारी है।

title: Taliban's 'No Women' Diktat In Delhi Sparks Political Firestorm | India Today News
description:
A major political controversy has erupted in New Delhi over a press interaction by Afghanistan's acting Foreign Minister, Amir Khan Muttaqi, where women journalists were reportedly barred. Trinamool Congress MP Mahua Moitra stated, 'This is the ultimate dishonour to the women of India that our government has participated in this, has been a willing participant, has used taxpayers money to fund this exercise where women journalists who have been asked to leave the room.' The incident, which took place at the Afghan Embassy, has drawn sharp criticism from opposition leaders, including Moitra and the Congress's Priyanka Gandhi Vadra, who are questioning the government's tolerance of such misogyny on Indian soil. In response, the Ministry of External Affairs issued a clarification, stating it had no involvement in the event as it was organized by the Afghan side on its own embassy premises.

title: #bbm #news #politics #prrd #vpsara
Trump to pay is US troops amid Government shutdown, orders Pete Hegseth after Chuck Schumer’s remark
description:
US President Donald Trump said his administration found a way to pay troops during the federal government shutdown. POTUS ‘ordered his Secretary of War’ Pete Hegseth to pay troops, which they will be waiting, on October 15th. “We have identified funds to do this, and Secretary Hegseth will use them to PAY OUR TROOPS”, Said Trump. However, he did not identify funding sources or the total amount that would be used for troop salaries. Trump made announcement on 11th day of Govt shutdown sparked by funding impasse with minority congressional Democrats. Earlier, Chuck Schumer said that Democrats, brave troops will miss the paychecks they are rightfully due on October 15th. “Will not allow Democrats to hold our Military, and entire Security of our Nation, HOSTAGE”, Said President Trump.

title: DK Shivakumar News | "Can Do Politics Without You": DK Shivakumar Loses Cool Over Media Report
description:
Deputy Chief Minister DK Shivakumar has asserted he's "not in a hurry" for a promotion amid a renewed buzz of leadership change in Karnataka. Accusing the media of twisting his statement, he denied saying that the time has come for him to become the Chief Minister.

"Some media houses are twisting my statement and are trying to create a controversy. I have never said that it is time for me to become the Chief Minister. I'll file a defamation case if anyone twists my statement and broadcasts it," he told reporters.

title: María Corina Machado Wins Nobel 2025 | Democracy Champion of Venezuela | News9
description:
Venezuelan opposition leader María Corina Machado, now in hiding, has been awarded the 2025 Nobel Peace Prize for her relentless fight to restore democracy in Venezuela. Known as Venezuela’s Iron Lady and recently named among Time Magazine’s ‘100 Most Influential People of 2025,’ Machado dedicated her award to former U.S. President Donald Trump, praising his support for Venezuela’s democratic movement. The Nobel Committee called her a “brave and committed champion of peace” striving for a just transition from dictatorship.

title: YS Sharmila Sparks Controversy over TTD Temple Plan 🔥 | AP Politics News
description:
WATCH: YS Sharmila’s Explosive Comments on TTD Temple Project 🔥 | Congress in Trouble | BJP Hits Back | AP Politics 2025

Big controversy in Andhra Pradesh! 💥
APCC Chief YS Sharmila has sparked a major political storm by criticizing the TTD decision to build 5,000 temples in Dalit colonies. She accused CM Chandrababu Naidu of spreading RSS ideology and demanded TTD funds be used for roads, schools, and hospitals instead of temples.

Her remarks created a political earthquake ⚡ — with BJP leaders demanding an apology, calling her statements “anti-Hindu.” Even Congress High Command is reportedly upset, fearing her comments could alienate Dalit voters and hurt the party’s revival plans in Andhra Pradesh.

🔥 Key Highlights:
1️⃣ YS Sharmila attacks TTD and CM Chandrababu.
2️⃣ BJP slams her for hurting Hindu sentiments.
3️⃣ Congress high command angry over her remarks.
4️⃣ Dalit community reactions mixed across AP.
5️⃣ Political tension rises in Tirupati & Amaravati.

description:
WATCH: YS Sharmila’s Explosive Comments on TTD Temple Project 🔥 | Congress in Trouble | BJP Hits Back | AP Politics 2025

Big controversy in Andhra Pradesh! 💥
APCC Chief YS Sharmila has sparked a major political storm by criticizing the TTD decision to build 5,000 temples in Dalit colonies. She accused CM Chandrababu Naidu of spreading RSS ideology and demanded TTD funds be used for roads, schools, and hospitals instead of temples.

Her remarks created a political earthquake ⚡ — with BJP leaders demanding an apology, calling her statements “anti-Hindu.” Even Congress High Command is reportedly upset, fearing her comments could alienate Dalit voters and hurt the party’s revival plans in Andhra Pradesh.

1️⃣ YS Sharmila attacks TTD and CM Chandrababu.

description:
पवन सिंह–ज्योति सिंह विवाद गहराया: गंभीर आरोपों के बीच करवा चौथ पर भावनात्मक पोस्ट

भोजपुरी स्टार पवन सिंह और उनकी पत्नी ज्योति सिंह के बीच चल रहा विवाद अब और गहराता जा रहा है। ज्योति सिंह ने अभिनेता पर गर्भपात कराने और मानसिक प्रताड़ना जैसे गंभीर आरोप लगाए हैं, जबकि पवन सिंह ने इन आरोपों को सिरे से खारिज करते हुए कानूनी कार्रवाई की बात कही है। करवा चौथ पर ज्योति ने खुद को ‘अभागन’ बताया और हाल ही में प्रशांत किशोर से मुलाकात की। वहीं, पवन सिंह ने बिहार विधानसभा चुनाव 2025 न लड़ने का ऐलान किया है।

description:
🚨 Cough Syrup Controversy in India 🚨

Tragic news from Madhya Pradesh: multiple children under 5 have died after consuming contaminated cough syrups containing toxic chemicals like diethylene glycol (DEG) and ethylene glycol (EG). The syrups, including Coldrif and Nextro-DS, were found to have dangerously high levels of these substances.

The manufacturer, Sresan Pharmaceuticals, is under investigation, and authorities have taken strict action, including bans and arrests. Health experts and the Indian Academy of Paediatrics urge caution, emphasizing that these deaths were due to adulterated medicines, not medical negligence.

⚠️ Public Advisory: Parents and caregivers should avoid giving cough syrups to young children without consulting a healthcare professional.

Stay informed and share this important update.

description:
WATCH: YS Sharmila’s Explosive Comments on TTD Temple Project 🔥 | Congress in Trouble | BJP Hits Back | AP Politics 2025

Big controversy in Andhra Pradesh! 💥
APCC Chief YS Sharmila has sparked a major political storm by criticizing the TTD decision to build 5,000 temples in Dalit colonies. She accused CM Chandrababu Naidu of spreading RSS ideology and demanded TTD funds be used for roads, schools, and hospitals instead of temples.

Her remarks created a political earthquake ⚡ — with BJP leaders demanding an apology, calling her statements “anti-Hindu.” Even Congress High Command is reportedly upset, fearing her comments could alienate Dalit voters and hurt the party’s revival plans in Andhra Pradesh.

1️⃣ YS Sharmila attacks TTD and CM Chandrababu.

description:
WATCH: YS Sharmila’s Explosive Comments on TTD Temple Project 🔥 | Congress in Trouble | BJP Hits Back | AP Politics 2025

Big controversy in Andhra Pradesh! 💥
APCC Chief YS Sharmila has sparked a major political storm by criticizing the TTD decision to build 5,000 temples in Dalit colonies. She accused CM Chandrababu Naidu of spreading RSS ideology and demanded TTD funds be used for roads, schools, and hospitals instead of temples.

Her remarks created a political earthquake ⚡ — with BJP leaders demanding an apology, calling her statements “anti-Hindu.” Even Congress High Command is reportedly upset, fearing her comments could alienate Dalit voters and hurt the party’s revival plans in Andhra Pradesh.

1️⃣ YS Sharmila attacks TTD and CM Chandrababu.
